      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new horror anthology and i'm stuck on the setting for one of my stories. i want to write something about a 'haunted' urban neighborhood—the kind of place that feels heavy and dangerous even before you encounter anything supernatural. can you help me brainstorm some atmospheric details or themes for a place like that?",
